<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idca6d522f-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70" identifier="/us/usc/t49/s321"><num value="321">§ 321.</num><heading> Definitions</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">In this subchapter, “aeronautics”, “air commerce”, and “air navigation facility” have the same meanings given those terms in <ref href="/us/usc/t49/s40102/a">section 40102(a) of this title</ref>.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idca6d5230-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70">(<ref href="/us/pl/97/449/s1/b">Pub. L. 97–449, § 1(b)</ref>, <date date="1983-01-12">Jan. 12, 1983</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/96/2422">96 Stat. 2422</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/98/216/s2/2">Pub. L. 98–216, § 2(2)</ref>, <date date="1984-02-14">Feb. 14, 1984</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/98/5">98 Stat. 5</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/103/272/s5/m/8">Pub. L. 103–272, § 5(m)(8)</ref>, <date date="1994-07-05">July 5, 1994</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/108/1376">108 Stat. 1376</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/103/429/s6/2">Pub. L. 103–429, § 6(2)</ref>, <date date="1994-10-31">Oct. 31, 1994</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/108/4378">108 Stat. 4378</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
